pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Zambiri zomwe zili pa bolodi ili zimasonkhanitsidwa mwachindunji kuchokera ku mayankho a kafukufuku ndipo sizichokera ku ziwerengero zovomerezeka zamayiko kapena ma data. Ikuyimira malingaliro omwe achinyamata akuwonetsa panthawi ya kafukufukuyu, ndipo malingaliro aliwonse ochokera ku mayankhowa ali ndi udindo wa wogwiritsa ntchito, osati PMNCH. PMNCH ikudzipereka kulemekeza, kulimbikitsa ndi kuteteza ufulu ndi ubwino wa anthu onse. Malingaliro aliwonse omwe aperekedwa muzoyankha pa kafukufukuyu kapena zolembedwa zotuluka m'dashboard iyi zomwe zikusemphana ndi kudziperekaku sizikuvomerezedwa ndi PMNCH.
